hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I came here to study dexlansoprazole daily dosage In defence of my teenage self, parts of the self-indulgent monologues weren’t badly written, but they are a far cry from Malala’s eloquence and fierce passion. She had the audience applauding her on their feet as she left the stage on Sunday night, and when she touched her heart three times with her right hand in response to our ovation, it done with such genuine emotion that I felt my eyes water.
